<h4>Lower Headings</h4>
<p>
	The following headlines have the same values across all screen sizes, mobile,
	tablet, desktop.
</p>

<table>
	<thead>
	<tr>
		<th>Style Preview</th>
		<th>Links</th>
		<th>Usage</th>
	</tr>
	</thead>
	<tbody>
	<tr>
		<td class="chapter not-content">
			<Headline type="chapter">Chapter</Headline>
		</td>
		<td>
			Metric2 / semi-bold / scale 4
		</td>
		<td>
			<p>For in-page titles / chapters</p>
			<p>Usage Examples: <a
				href="https://www.ft.com/content/844ed28c-8074-4856-bde0-20f3bf4cd8f0#:~:text=gaming.%20Tom%20Braithwaite-,1.%20Amazon,-SECTOR%3A%20ECOMMERCE%20/%20HQ">FT
