				href="https://www.ft.com/content/40413894-3612-4228-8435-fb6af2659eb2#:~:text=AGO07%3A50-,Labour%20blames%20government%20finances%20for%20ditching%20%C2%A328bn%20green%20investment%20plan,-Donato%20Paolo%20Mancini">Live
				News</a></p>
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="subheading not-content">
			<Headline type="subheading">Subheading</Headline>
		</td>
		<td>
			Metric2 / regular / scale 4
		</td>
		<td>
			<p>For in-page sub-titles / sub-headings</p>
			<p>Usage Example: <a
				href="https://www.ft.com/content/2489a831-7a4b-4bcb-96ec-2c9c1d4ebe8e#:~:text=for%20all%20palates.-,The%20Salad%20Project,-1%20OLD%20BROAD">FT
				Globetrotter</a></p>
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="label not-content">
			<Headline type="label">LABEL</Headline>
		</td>
		<td>
			Metric2 / regular / scale 0
		</td>
		<td
		><p>To provide short details about a chapter, kickers (additional headline)
			just above a chapter.</p>

			<p>Usage Examples: <a href="https://www.ft.com/content/844ed28c-8074-4856-bde0-20f3bf4cd8f0#:~:text=SECTOR%3A%20ECOMMERCE%20/%20HQ%3A%20SEATTLE%2C%20US">FT Series</a>, <a href="https://www.ft.com/content/82574e3d-1633-48ad-8afb-71ebb3fe3dee#:~:text=promised%20the%20world.-,EARLY%20WARNINGS,-The%20virus%20arrives">kickers</a></p>
		</td>
	</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

